{"arkId":"cl010490821","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010490821","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Coffret-\u00e9critoire","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Coffret-\u00e9critoire"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : apr\u00e8s 1697","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 605 - Stavros S. Niarchos, Vitrine 22","room":"Salle 605, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1697,"endYear":"","imprecision":"apr\u00e8s","text":"Fin du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Patin, Jacques","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RFML.OA.2021.28.1","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"\u00e9critoire ; orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Le coffret rectangulaire sur \u00e2me de bois est enti\u00e8rement recouvert de chagrin noir, agr\u00e9ment\u00e9 de plaques d\u2019argent. Il repose sur quatre pieds d\u2019argent en forme de griffes de lion, pos\u00e9es sur un coussin, prolong\u00e9\u00e9s par une touffe d\u2019acanthe . Le couvercle ouvre \u00e0 deux charni\u00e8res agr\u00e9ment\u00e9es de plaques d\u2019argent cisel\u00e9es d\u2019une sphinge et de feuilles d\u2019acanthe.\r\nLe dessus du couvercle porte en son centre une grande plaque d\u2019argent, cisel\u00e9e de motifs v\u00e9g\u00e9taux et de deux cornes d\u2019abondance avec au centre\u2019un vase de fleurs, des rinceaux d\u2019acanthe et deux m\u00e9daillons accol\u00e9s, qui portent aujourd\u2019hui les chiffres CM et ST . Sur le devant du  couvercle une applique d\u2019argent, cisel\u00e9e d\u2019une t\u00eate de Midas \r\nSur les faces, plaques d\u0027argent \u00e0 d\u00e9cor de feuillages, acanthes, et fruits. la fermeture est assur\u00e9e par un crochet agr\u00e9ment\u00e9 de filets et d\u2019une t\u00eate de brebis qui vient coulisser dans une plaque cisel\u00e9e de deux t\u00eates de b\u00e9lier dispos\u00e9es dos \u00e0 dos.\r\n\u00c0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur, deux compartiments \u00e0 abattants couverts de chagrin noir destin\u00e9s l\u2019un aux plumes, l\u2019autre au papier, ainsi qu\u2019un abattant servant de table \u00e0 \u00e9crire. Deux cornets cubiques en argent sont log\u00e9s de part et d\u2019autre du compartiment des plumes : l\u2019encrier et le poudrier.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Ma\u00eetre : fleur de lis couronn\u00e9e, deux grains, lettres IP et un c\u0153ur avec une flamme au-dessus, pour Jacques Patin \u00e0 partir de 1697","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"12,4","displayDimension":"12,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"37,5","displayDimension":"37,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"28,2","displayDimension":"28,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : bois (recouvert de cuir)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : argent","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Vente Paris, Drouot, Tajan, 29 mai 2000, n\u00b0 138 ; collection Bernard de Leye, Bruxelles, don Mr Bernard de Leye, 2021","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"de Leye,  Bernard","note":"","role":", Antiquaire \/ Marchand d\u0027art"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don manuel","doubt":"","d